{"id":9082,"date":"2021-06-10T12:26:50","date_gmt":"2021-06-10T12:26:50","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/?page_id=9082"},"modified":"2023-02-02T09:15:14","modified_gmt":"2023-02-02T09:15:14","slug":"alumni-relations","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/success\/alumni-relations\/","title":{"rendered":"Alumni Relations"},"content":{"rendered":"\n\n<!-- hero -->\n<section class=\"subpage-hero-section\" style=\"background: url('https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/DSC_7714-2.jpg') center center no-repeat; background-size:cover;background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.4); background-blend-mode: overlay;\">\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-10 offset-lg-1\">\n               <h1 data-aos=\"fade-up\" class=\"subpage-hero-h\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF\">Alumni Relations<\/h1>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n\n\n<!-- image section -->\n\n<section class=\"image-section   \">\n    <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-5 offset-lg-1\">\n                                  \n                <img class=\"w-100 blue-frame blue-frame\" src=\"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/DSC_7697-2-e1622041292632.jpg\" alt=\"\" \/>\n                \n                            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"col-lg-4 offset-lg-1 align-items-center d-flex\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\n                <div class=\"w-100\">\n                <h2 class=\"section-h blue\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">Alumni<\/h1>\n                <p class=\"section-p\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">Halcyon\u2019s alumni community is growing and flourishing. As of 2021, we are celebrating four graduation classes, and continuing to nurture our lifelong connections with these members of our community who are fulfilling their aspirations every day. <br><br>\r\nIt is through the creation of an international, diverse, and rewarding environment that our students can grow and challenge themselves as learners, leaders, and change-makers.\r\n<br><br>\r\nAt Halcyon we are inspired by the close community we have created and see it as central to everything we do. Even as you flourish in the next chapter in your life, you are still &#8211; and always will be &#8211; a part of that community, wherever you are in the world, and whatever your original connection with our wonderful school: be it student, parent, donor or staff member.<br><br>\r\nAs our alumni numbers grow, so will our programme &#8211; and we are pleased to already share our updates and events with you through our alumni newsletter and our social media channels.\r\n<\/p>\n                                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:40px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n\n<!-- hero -->\n<section class=\"title-section\">\n            <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n                <div class=\"row\">\n                    <div class=\"col-lg-6 offset-lg-3\">\n                        <h2 data-aos=\"fade-up\" class=\"section-p m-0 text-center\">\n                            <h2 class=\"section-h blue\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">Going Forward<\/h2>\r\n<p class=\"section-p\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\r\nWe plan to introduce more events and opportunities in the very near future, including a reunion event to celebrate the fifth anniversary of our Class of 2017 &#8211; our first graduating class &#8211; in 2022.\r\n<br><br> \r\nWe would love you to be a core part of our alumni society, creating a lively global network of like-minded and inspiring people that strengthen Halcyon&#8217;s current community. Your voice is central to our future: if you have any ideas for what you would like to see as part of the alumni programme, or have any feedback on any aspect of alumni relations at the school, please email <a href=\"mailto:development@halcyonschool.com\">Olivia Ceballos, our Development Lead<\/a>.<br><br>\r\nIf any of your contact details have changed or you would like to update us on any of your news, please complete <a href=\"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/halcyon-alumni-survey-2021\">this form<\/a>.                           \n                        <\/h2>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/section>\n\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:40px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"459\" src=\"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Halcyoncampus-108-2-1024x459.jpg\" alt=\"alumni halcyon doors\" data-id=\"9121\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Halcyoncampus-108-2-scaled.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/?attachment_id=9121\" class=\"wp-image-9121\" srcset=\"https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Halcyoncampus-108-2-1024x459.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Halcyoncampus-108-2-300x135.jpg 300w, https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Halcyoncampus-108-2-768x344.jpg 768w, https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Halcyoncampus-108-2-1536x689.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Halcyoncampus-108-2-2048x918.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/halcyonschool.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Halcyoncampus-108-2-600x269.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loadin